**Detailed Technical Design Specification**

## Core Type Extensions

### 1. Enhanced DevlogEntry Interface
```typescript
export interface DevlogEntry {
  // ... existing fields ...

  // Hierarchy fields
  parentId?: DevlogId;           // Parent project/epic ID
  childIds: DevlogId[];          // Child epic/task IDs
  hierarchyLevel: HierarchyLevel; // project | epic | task
  rootProjectId?: DevlogId;      // Root project for quick lookups

  // Planning fields
  estimatedHours?: number;       // Time estimate
  actualHours?: number;          // Time spent
  startDate?: string;            // Planned start date
  dueDate?: string;              // Planned completion date
  iteration?: string;            // Sprint/iteration name
  milestone?: string;            // Milestone name

  // Enhanced dependency tracking
  blockedBy: DevlogId[];         // Entries that block this one
  blocks: DevlogId[];            // Entries this one blocks
  criticalPath: boolean;         // Is this on the critical path?
}
```

### 2. Project Template System
```typescript
export interface ProjectTemplate {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  description: string;
  structure: ProjectTemplateNode[];
}

export interface ProjectTemplateNode {
  title: string;
  type: DevlogType;
  description?: string;
  estimatedHours?: number;
  children?: ProjectTemplateNode[];
}
```

### 3. Progress Rollup System
```typescript
export interface ProjectProgress {
  totalTasks: number;
  completedTasks: number;
  completionPercentage: number;
  estimatedHours: number;
  actualHours: number;
  criticalPathStatus: 'on-track' | 'at-risk' | 'delayed';
}
```

**üß† AI-Native Project Management Framework Design**

## Core Paradigm Shifts:

### 1. **Complexity-Based Planning (Not Time-Based)**
```typescript
interface TaskComplexity {
  cognitiveLoad: 'trivial' | 'simple' | 'moderate' | 'complex' | 'research';
  contextRequirement: 'local' | 'cross-file' | 'cross-module' | 'system-wide';
  toolDependency: 'basic' | 'standard' | 'specialized' | 'external-api';
  uncertaintyLevel: 'known' | 'exploratory' | 'research' | 'experimental';
}
```

### 2. **Session-Based Velocity (Not Sprint-Based)**
```typescript
interface AIVelocity {
  problemsSolvedPerSession: number;
  averageContextSwitchCost: number;  // tokens to rebuild context
  successRate: number;               // % of attempts that succeed
  iterationsToSolution: number;      // avg attempts needed
}
```

### 3. **Token Economics & Context Management**
```typescript
interface SessionCapacity {
  maxTokensPerSession: number;
  contextWindowUtilization: number;
  toolCallsPerSession: number;
  persistentContextSize: number;    // devlog context overhead
}
```

### 4. **Knowledge-Based Dependencies (Not Coordination-Based)**
```typescript
interface AIDependency {
  type: 'knowledge' | 'data' | 'tool' | 'context' | 'capability';
  description: string;
  blockingReason: 'missing-info' | 'incomplete-context' | 'tool-limitation';
  resolutionStrategy: 'research' | 'incremental' | 'parallel' | 'deferred';
}
```

### 5. **Outcome-Driven Progress (Not Status-Driven)**
```typescript
interface AIProgress {
  knowledgeGained: string[];         // What the AI learned
  contextBuilt: string[];            // Context accumulated
  capabilitiesUnlocked: string[];    // New tools/abilities gained
  problemsSolved: string[];          // Actual outcomes
  uncertaintiesResolved: string[];   // Clarifications made
}
```
